To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AccumulationDistributionOscillator _adosc;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_adosc = ADOSC(symbol, fastPeriod, slowPeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_adosc.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "accumulationdistributionoscillator", _adosc.Current.Value);
}
